        "created_at": "2019-07-09T11:28:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=1077145\"><strong>2009 Bernard Dugat-Py Vosne-Roman\u00e9e Vieilles Vignes</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Nuits, Vosne-Roman\u00e9e (7/9/2019)</em><br>\nHeavily reduced and supremely youthful. Plenty of meat and musk that makes way for intense black and red fruits with air. There\u2019s some floral spice and lots of tar. It has serious build, is deep and very long. Needs a couple of decades.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
